Nginx
-----

This formula depends on :doc:`Nginx </nginx/doc/index>` to make it available
over `HTTP <http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Http>`_ on port ``80`` or
`HTTPS <http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Https>`_ over port ``443``

.. note::

  `SSL <http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Secure_Sockets_Layer>`_ is used only if you
  specified ``ssl`` key in your formula's pillars keys.

Please check :doc:`Nginx pillar doc </nginx/doc/firewall>` for details.
